snippet.title: Mariah Carey's voice cracks horribly and sounds awful singing 'All I Want For Christmas is You'

localized.description:
Mariah Carey sang her modern Christmas classic 'All I Want for Christmas Is You' at the National Christmas Tree Lighting event in Washington, D.C. last week.

Her voice cracked throughout the performance, and she sounded like she was sick. It was really bad, which is shocking for Mimi. For the top half of the performance, Carey sounded winded — and she missed more than a few notes. But it was cold and she was outside, so we'll cut her some slack there.
